---
const workshopImages = [
  "/gambar-workshop/kiriatas1.png",
  "/gambar-workshop/kananatas2.jpeg",
  "/gambar-workshop/kiribawah3.png",
  "/gambar-workshop/kananbawah4.png"
];
---

<section id="workshop" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#0A0A0A] overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container-main max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 xl:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Left Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col text-left">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="inline-block text-[#FFE600] font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-5">
            WORKSHOP KAMI
          </span>
          <h2 class="font-display text-white text-[3rem] sm:text-[4rem] lg:text-[4.5rem] xl:text-[5rem] leading-[0.9] uppercase tracking-tight">
            TEMPAT DI MANA SEPATU DAN<br class="hidden lg:block"/> AKSESORIS KEMBALI BERSIH
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-[#A1A1A1] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl">
          Setiap item ditangani langsung di workshop KUCEK.SHOES dengan proses cleaning yang aman, teliti, dan profesional. Dari sepatu harian hingga koleksi favorit pelanggan.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-6">
          {[
            "Workshop aktif setiap hari",
            "Proses pengerjaan detail dan aman",
            "Ratusan item telah ditangani"
          ].map((point) => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-white/90 text-lg">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#FFE600]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#FFE600] font-bold text-sm">
                ✓
              </span>
              {point}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Gallery -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-5 mt-10 lg:mt-0">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5 pt-0 lg:pt-10">
          <div class="group relative rounded-[20px] overflow-hidden border border-[#FFE600]/10 hover:border-[#FFE600]/50 transition-colors duration-500 bg-[#111]">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <img src={workshopImages[0]} alt="Workshop view" class="w-full h-32 md:h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="group relative rounded-[20px] overflow-hidden border border-[#FFE600]/10 hover:border-[#FFE600]/50 transition-colors duration-500 bg-[#111]">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <img src={workshopImages[2]} alt="Cleaning process" class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5">
          <div class="group relative rounded-[20px] overflow-hidden border border-[#FFE600]/10 hover:border-[#FFE600]/50 transition-colors duration-500 bg-[#111]">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <img src={workshopImages[1]} alt="Shoe rack" class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="group relative rounded-[20px] overflow-hidden border border-[#FFE600]/10 hover:border-[#FFE600]/50 transition-colors duration-500 bg-[#111]">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <img src={workshopImages[3]} alt="Details cleaning" class="w-full h-32 md:h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
